title: Gay

Gay is defined as being attracted to the same gender, and is often used as a synonym for [[homosexual|Homosexual]]. In the context of a gay male, the term [[androsexual|Androsexual]] can be used. In the context of a gay female, the terms [[lesbian|Lesbian]] and [[gynesexual|Gynesexual]] can be used. Gay can also be used as an umbrella term for the LGBTQ+ community.